results.description:
Add More Space To Your Kitchen By Utilizing A Custom Noodle Board Stove Cover, Sink Cover, or Serving Tray!

Noodle Board Dimensions: 22'' x 29.5'' - Works With Most Standard Ovens
***Make Sure to Pre-Measure Your Stove Before Ordering to Ensure a Perfect Fit. If you need a custom-sized noodle board, please message us with the details & we will be happy to build it for you.

Sink Cover Dimensions: 16.5'' x 33'' - Works With Most Standard Sinks
***Make Sure to Pre-Measure Your Sink Before Ordering to Ensure a Perfect Fit. If you need a custom-sized sink cover, please message us with the details & we will be happy to build it for you.

Serving Tray Dimensions: 16.5" x 22"

Material: Pine Planks With Your Stain Color of Choice + Our Love Design!

Natural (No Stain)
Natural W/ Aqua Wash
Ebony
Ebony W/ Aqua Wash
Walnut
Dark Walnut
Cherry
Smoke
Black
Weathered Gray
Blush Faux Cedar

More Colors to Come! If you don't see the color you need listed here, just send us a message and we will do our best to match it for you!

Every order is made by hand and crafted so that every piece is one-of-a-kind. Each board shows the natural knots, seams, splits, etc. to keep the rustic farmhouse authenticity alive.

As every piece of wood is different, each board will react differently to the stain, making your custom piece perfectly unique! Variations are to be expected as some colors require "aging"/time to achieve their optimum coloring. Buy with confidence - you will not be disappointed!

As each piece is custom ordered, we do not accept returns, but rest assured you will love what you receive. We truly appreciate your business and look forward to creating a custom order for you!

Please note that these products are not intended to be used as a cutting board; they are not food-grade safe and as such should be used for no other purpose than storage / decoration.

Aftercare:
To keep your board in good shape, let oven & stove-top cool completely before replacing it on the stove-top. Hot temperatures could cause the board to warp / crack, etc. We cannot be held responsible for any damage resulting from misuse of this product. If anything should get on your noodle board, wipe clean with a soft wet cloth - pat dry. Avoid the use of anything abrasive as it will damage the stain and wood underneath. We hope that you love your custom piece for years to come!

💕  How do I take care of returns, exchanges or product issue? 💕 
💕 TRACKING SHOWS ARRIVED
There’s not a whole lot we can do when the tracking info shows it as being delivered. Please check with everyone in your household as someone else might have brought it in. Sometimes we have heard of a package going to a neighbor mistakenly or being left at a different/side door. In our experience, usually the package is located.
Most orders are shipped via UPS Mail Innovations or UPS Surepost, and final delivery is by the USPS so we also suggest having the customer contact their local post office and many times they can get in touch with the actual person who delivered it and see if they recall where they left it. It’s best to do that soon after it’s marked as delivered.
💕 NO TRACKING OR NO MOVEMENT
If a package does not show any movement and has passed the allotted time for delivery we will send a new package at our cost to the customer.  We may ask you to check to very the address or supply us with a new shipping address.
SIZING EXCHANGE
We don't offer exchanges or refunds in those situations.
💕 PRODUCT ISSUE
If it is an issue on our end where we sent out the wrong product, wrong size, bad graphic just send us a picture of what you have  received for quality control purposes and we can offer a refund or replacement once the issue is deemed our fault.
US customers have up to 30 days after the shipped date and international customers have up to 60 days after the shipped date.
What we need to make a replacement order:
1.	Please provide the name and email.
2.	Please provide the order number.
3.	Please provide picture of wrong/ damaged item And Shipping Label.
Once we receive this we will print a replacement product and send it right out!
